WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.433 --> 00:00:05.100
Einstein may be the brightest
mind I have yet taught.

00:00:05.100 --> 00:00:06.266
He's a menace!

00:00:06.266 --> 00:00:07.867
[explosion]

00:00:07.867 --> 00:00:10.200
You are skipping classes and
challenging your instructors.

00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:12.165
What I want to
know, Sir, is why.

00:00:12.166 --> 00:00:13.967
My name is Professor
Philipp Lenard.

00:00:13.967 --> 00:00:15.166
Herr Professor.

00:00:15.166 --> 00:00:16.667
Mileva Maric.

00:00:16.667 --> 00:00:18.433
One doesn't lose track of
the sole woman in the room.

00:00:18.433 --> 00:00:21.166
She's up all night,
filling her brain with things

00:00:21.166 --> 00:00:22.467
I can't begin to understand.

00:00:22.467 --> 00:00:23.834
Then how do you know
she understands them?

00:00:23.834 --> 00:00:27.166
I'm head over heels
in love with your mind.

00:00:27.166 --> 00:00:29.500
You're my partner
in life and love

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:31.166
and endless scientific pursuit.

00:00:31.166 --> 00:00:32.400
How is Marie?

00:00:32.400 --> 00:00:33.766
Everyone is quite excited.

00:00:33.767 --> 00:00:34.734
About what?

00:00:34.734 --> 00:00:35.834
The courtship, of course.

00:00:35.834 --> 00:00:36.934
The potential of it!

00:00:36.934 --> 00:00:38.367
I'm going to be a professor.

00:00:38.367 --> 00:00:39.800
I will think for
thinking's sake.

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:42.367
That is the most indulgent
thing I've ever heard.

00:00:42.367 --> 00:00:44.666
Well, don't leave
like this, Albert.

00:00:44.667 --> 00:00:45.767
Liar!

00:00:45.767 --> 00:00:48.600
How could you be so
careless with my heart?

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:50.266
Physics should
be an adventure.

00:00:50.266 --> 00:00:51.667
That's enough!

00:00:51.667 --> 00:00:52.667
Fail him if you must.

00:00:52.667 --> 00:00:54.400
I am no longer concerned
for his future.

00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:55.100
Mitta!

00:00:55.100 --> 00:00:56.333
Hello, Papa.

00:00:56.333 --> 00:00:57.934
I'm so sorry, Papa.

00:00:57.934 --> 00:01:00.333
I failed you.

